name: Perception.
description:
Perception is unique. People look at us differently. It doesn't matter because it doesn't change who we are. It's the same for this piece. If you return it, it will always be the same piece, with a different perception. Don't change who you are by the way people look at you. You're unique.

This piece has been created on Procreate Pocket. Sketch and timelapse are available on request !
